PrecisAmendments to the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1989 which will allow the Ontario Minister of Natural Resources to amend the terms and conditions of licences, other than recreational or sport fishing licences, and establish the procedures for doing so, restrict fishing from a boat once possession limits are reached, establish a number of fish sanctuaries, and revise the definition of "angling" and the scientific description of "walleye".
